itto</span><span>, </span></li><li><span class="hlFld-ContribAuthor">Roberto Grassi</span></li></ul></div><div class="meta">1 September 2014</div></div><div class="getFTR external-links"><div class="core-xlink-crossref"><a href="https://doi.org/10.1007/978-3-319-08192-2_1">Crossref</a></div></div></li><li class="citedByEntry" data-doi="10.1007/978-3-319-08192-2_10"><div class="related"><div class="related__title"><a target="_blank" href="https://doi.org/10.1007/978-3-319-08192-2_10">MDCT Imaging of Blunt Traumatic Bowel and Colonic Perforation</a></div><div class="related__authors"><ul class="rlist--inline loa mobile-authors loa-height"><li><span class="hlFld-ContribAuthor">Francesco Iaselli</span><span>, </span></li><li><span class="hlFld-ContribAuthor">Isabella Iadevito</span><span>, </span></li><li><span class="hlFld-ContribAuthor">Franco Guida</span><span>, </span></li><li><span class="hlFld-ContribAuthor">Giacomo Sica</span><span>, </span></li><li><span class="hlFld-ContribAuthor">Giorgio Bocchini</span><span>, </span></li><li><span class="hlFld-ContribAuthor">Mariano Scaglione</span></li></ul></div><div class="meta">1 September 2014</div></div><div class="getFTR external-links"><div class="core-xlink-crossref"><a href="https://doi.org/10.1007/978-3-319-08192-2_10">Crossref</a></div></div></li><li class="citedByEntry" data-doi="10.1007/978-3-319-08192-2_5"><div class="related"><div class="related__title"><a target="_blank" href="https://doi.org/10.1007/978-3-319-08192-2_5">Role of Multidetector Row Computed Tomography in the Diagnosis of Gastroduodenal Perforation</a></div><div class="related__authors"><ul class="rlist--inline loa mobile-authors loa-height"><li><span class="hlFld-ContribAuthor">Daniela Vecchione</span><span>, </span></li><li><span class="hlFld-ContribAuthor">Giovanna Russo</span><span>, </span></li><li><span class="hlFld-ContribAuthor">Raffaella Niola</span></li></ul></div><div class="meta">1 September 2014</div></div><div class="getFTR externa